ENTERPRISE EDITION FEATURES:

Certain features in this software are labeled as "Enterprise" features and 
are designed to work with Oracle Database Enterprise Edition. These features
may require appropriate Oracle Database Enterprise Edition licenses for 
production use:

- Oracle Advanced Security (TDE, VPD)
- Oracle Database Vault
- Oracle Partitioning
- Oracle Advanced Compression
- Oracle AWR (Automatic Workload Repository)
- Oracle SQL Plan Management
- Oracle Resource Manager
- Oracle Fine-Grained Auditing

Users should consult Oracle's licensing documentation to determine their
licensing requirements for these features.

===============================================================================

MODEL CONTEXT PROTOCOL (MCP) INTEGRATION:

This software implements the Model Context Protocol (MCP) specification for
integration with AI systems and large language models. The MCP protocol
implementation is based on publicly available specifications and is designed
for interoperability with MCP-compatible AI systems.

